* :joDVCplPbOmC8UHw: Lai Ning (1973-1988), formerly known as Lai Lin , Sichuan Province City of Ya'an Shimian County One, the second grade students of junior high school living asbestos. In March 13, 1988, in order to put out the fire emergency, rescue village, TV satellite ground receiving station safety protection, he take the initiative to join the fire fighting team, fire fighting in the four or five hours after death. In 1988 May, the Communist Youth League Central Committee, the State Education Commission awarded the honorable title of "Heroes" of Lai Ning.
